# Creamy Tomato Soup

Based on [Chrissy Teigen Cravings](https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/252973/cravings-by-chrissy-teigen-with-adeena-sussman) ([archive](http://web.archive.org/web/20251202235345/https://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/books/252973/cravings-by-chrissy-teigen-with-adeena-sussman/)), pg. 45

